<tr>
<td> * <a style="width: 50em;" href="http://www.fly-ted.org/view/cgnumber">Browse by CG Number</a></td><td>Browse items in FlyTED by the cg number of genes.</td></tr>
<tr><td> * <a style="width: 50em;" href="http://www.fly-ted.org/view/strain">Browse by Strain</a></td><td>Browse items in FlyTED  by the meiotic arrest strain of fly used.</td></tr>
<tr><td> * <a style="width: 50em;" href="http://www.fly-ted.org/view/expression">Browse by Expression Location</a></td><td>Browse items in FlyTED  by the gene expression location defined by the <a href="http://obofoundry.org/cgi-bin/detail.cgi?id=fly_anatomy"><i>Drosophila</i> Anatomy Ontology</a>.</td></tr>
<tr><td> * <a style="width: 50em;" href="http://www.fly-ted.org/links.html">Related Links</a></td><td>Links to related <i>Drosophila</i> image collections and data.</td></tr>
<tr><td> * <a style="width: 50em;" href="http://www.fly-ted.org/meth.html">About the Dataset</a></td><td>Information about the dataset and the methodology used to create the gene expression images in FlyTED.</td></tr>
<tr><td> * <a style="width: 50em;" href="http://www.fly-ted.org/information.html">About the Database</a></td><td>Information about this database and its implementation.</td></tr>
